Titolo: MechWarrior 3

Anno: 1999

Descrizione: MechWarrior 3 is a vehicle simulation game, part of the MechWarrior series. It featured a new 3D accelerated graphics engine at the time of its release. The game contains over 20 missions, with access to 18 different mechs. A novelization called Trial Under Fire was written by Loren L. Coleman.

Genere: Vehicle simulation 

Valutazione: 77
